MATH_TST.PRG demonstrates the limitations in range and accuracy of the
SIF_MATH.S module. Numbers can be entered as decimal or hex numbers in
the appropriate box. Move from entry box to entry box by pressing the
cursor keys or clicking on the box. If entering hex numbers then all 8
digits must be entered. Number entry is terminated by pressing return.


* clears the entire entry.
/ backspaces.
shift_0 to shift_5 gives A to F for hex entry.
( quits the programme

Help gives the above information.


